                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Vegetarian: swap meat for roasted Mediterranean vegetables (courgette, pepper, aubergine) and crumbled feta."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
